data.description: Adorable home that can be a 2 or 3 bedroom, 2 bath. Located 1 block from downtown with large lot for parking to the east of the home. This home has original hardwood floors, tile kitchen, and carpeted bedrooms. Roof is approx. 5 years old. The location would also make a great office space!
